mg-responsive wp-image-6511\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/DSC_0191-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/DSC_0191.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-5\"><h2><strong>Mesa de ciencias<\/strong><\/h2>\n<hr \/>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Juegos did\u00e1cticos, observaci\u00f3n con microscopios y lupas\u00a0 una mesa de objetos naturales, calcos y sonidos de la naturaleza, para ver, o\u00edr y tocar. Un taller para asomarse, a trav\u00e9s de la experiencia, al maravilloso mundo de la colaboraci\u00f3n de las especies.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-9 fusion_builder_column_1_3 1_3 fusion-one-third fusion-column-last\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;width:30.6666%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\"><div class=\"fusion-image-element in-legacy-container\" style=\"--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-3 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\"Chocolate\" src=\"https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Chocolate.jpg\" alt class=\"img-responsive wp-image-6515\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Chocolate-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Chocolate.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-6\"><h2><strong>Taller de paletas de chocolate<\/strong><\/h2>\n<hr \/>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Un taller para hacer, saborear, oler y tocar, donde cada ni\u00f1o realiza su propia paleta de chocolate con forma la forma de Pun. Aprovechando al m\u00e1ximo las caracter\u00edsticas multisensoriales del material.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-10 fusion_builder_column_1_3 1_3 fusion-one-third fusion-column-first\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;width:30.6666%; margin-right: 4%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\"><div class=\"fusion-image-element in-legacy-container\" style=\"--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-4 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\"4\" src=\"https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/4.png\" alt class=\"img-responsive wp-image-6534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/4-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/4.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-7\"><h2><strong>Lectura y apreciaci\u00f3n<\/strong><\/h2>\n<hr \/>\n<p>Un espacio para leer, tocar, narrar y recorrer la historia a trav\u00e9s del dibujo.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-11 fusion_builder_column_1_3 1_3 fusion-one-third\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;width:30.6666%; margin-right: 4%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\"><div class=\"fusion-image-element in-legacy-container\" style=\"--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-5 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\"IVA\" src=\"https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/IVA.jpg\" alt class=\"img-responsive wp-image-6517\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/IVA-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.culturaenproyectos.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/IVA.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-8\"><h2><strong>Capacitaci\u00f3n docente<\/strong><\/h2>\n<hr \/>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Encuentros y talleres donde, a partir de <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pun y la m\u00fasica de la tierra<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, se reflexiona acerca de los distintos lenguajes en di\u00e1logo, la apreciaci\u00f3n con los sentidos a partir de un libro y su uso en las aulas.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fu